claim.claim-text:
1. A roller rolling machine making a sheet electrode with a predetermined thickness for an electric double layer capacitor by carrying out a rolling step, said machine comprising:
(a) A pair of rolling rollers;
(b) a winding section for winding up the rollers;
(c) a drawing section for drawing out the rollers;
(d) a tension control device for controlling tension of a sheet drawn out of the drawing section so that the tension on the sheet is constant;
(e) an edge position control device for controlling a widthwise position of the sheet, said edge position control device being located immediately before the rolling rollers;
(f) a winding side drive roller located adjacent to the winding section so as to be rotated at a predetermined speed; and
(g) a pressing element for applying a predetermined pressure to a drive roller on the winding side so that the winding section is pressed against the winding side drive roller.
